'''《王子與騎士》'''（''Prince & Knight''）是[[丹尼爾·哈克|丹尼爾·哈克]]（Daniel Haack）撰寫的兒童書，由史蒂維·劉易斯（Stevie Lewis）插畫。《王子和騎士》講述了一名年輕王子的故事，曾經愛上了一個騎士，在兩人一起工作後，舉行威脅王國的龍。<ref name=":0">{{Cite book|last=Haack|first=Daniel|title=Prince & Knight|publisher=Little Bee Books|year=2019}}</ref>

《王子與騎士》最初是由2018年的小蜜蜂出版的英語<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://littlebeebooks.com/books/prince-knight/|title=Prince & Knight|website=little bee books|language=en-US|access-date=2019-09-04|archive-date=2021-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210217042116/https://littlebeebooks.com/books/prince-knight/|dead-url=no}}</ref> ，是{{link-en|小蜜蜂出版社，美國|Bonnier Group}}和媒體宣傳群[[GLAAD|GLAAD]]之間的合作夥伴關係的努力。<ref name="#1">{{Cite web|title=GLAAD to Publish LGBTQ Book Series for Children|url=https://www.thewrap.com/glaad-to-publish-lgbtq-childrens-book-series-starting-with-prince-knight-exclusive/|date=2018-05-17|website=TheWrap|language=en-US|access-date=2019-09-04|archive-date=2020-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200918094136/https://www.thewrap.com/glaad-to-publish-lgbtq-childrens-book-series-starting-with-prince-knight-exclusive/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 夥伴關係在兒童文學中融合和提升LGBTQ的積極代表。 <ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=Prince & Knight' Puts A Gay-Inclusive Twist On Traditional Fairy Tales|url=https://www.huffpost.com/entry/prince-and-knight-gay-kids-book_n_5afd932fe4b0779345d6be89|last=Wong|first=Curtis|date=17 May 2018|website=HuffPost|access-date=2021-02-14|archive-date=2021-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309222813/https://www.huffpost.com/entry/prince-and-knight-gay-kids-book_n_5afd932fe4b0779345d6be89|dead-url=no}}</ref>該書還為加拿大和日本觀眾發表，並在發布後與陪伴書出版。<ref name=":2">{{Cite web|title=Daniel Haack (Press)|url=https://www.danielhaack.com/press|last=Haack|first=Daniel|access-date=2021-02-14|archive-date=2019-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191111192050/https://www.danielhaack.com/press|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

該書由於內容的性質而受到讚揚和反對，贏得了各種獎項，並應對了來自美國社會保守派的一些挑戰，這些保守派根據對兒童文學的適當性和道德性對兒童文學的恰當性和道德性提出了挑戰。

==情節 ==
從前，一位王子正排著他的王國的寶座，所以他的父母——國王和王后——決定他必須首先找到一位新娘來説明他統治。三人前往附近的王國，以滿足各種潛在的公主追求者，但王子沒有找到他正在尋找的公主三人見面。 

離開時，王子收到消息說一條龍正在攻擊他的王國。當騎士來協助時，王子衝回和怪物戰鬥。一起工作，騎士用他的盾牌蒙蔽了龍，讓王子成功地捕獲了野獸。然而，在這樣做，王子失去了他的平衡和下降。騎士騎馬沖去，抓住王子的手臂。

兩人感謝對方救了他們一命，墜入愛河。他們的婚姻得到了社區還有王子的父母的全力支持，他們為這對新人的婚禮歡呼雀躍。<ref name=":0" />

==出版社與背景==
《王子和騎士》於2018年5月1日首次以精裝本發行，作為小蜜蜂出版社與GLAAD合作領域的冠軍。此次發射受到新聞界的極大關注，包括[[芝加哥論壇報|芝加哥論壇報]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=16 LGBTQ children's books for Pride|url=https://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/books/ct-lgbtq-children-books-20180606-photogallery.html|website=chicagotribune.com|access-date=2019-09-04|archive-date=2021-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226002125/https://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/books/ct-lgbtq-children-books-20180606-photogallery.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> , {{link-en|男士風尚|Gay Time}}<ref>{{Cite web|title=GLAAD set to publish four LGBTQ children's books starting with a gay love story between a prince and a knight|url=https://www.gaytimes.co.uk/culture/106606/glaad-set-to-publish-four-lgbtq-childrens-book-starting-with-gay-love-story-between-a-prince-and-a-knight/|date=2018-05-19|website=Gay Times|language=en-GB|access-date=2019-09-04|archive-date=2019-09-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190904040243/https://www.gaytimes.co.uk/culture/106606/glaad-set-to-publish-four-lgbtq-childrens-book-starting-with-gay-love-story-between-a-prince-and-a-knight/|dead-url=no}}</ref> ,{{link-en|美國標誌電視臺|Logo TV}} <ref>{{Cite web|title=This LGBT-Friendly Children's Book From GLAAD Will Make Your Day {{!}} NewNowNext|url=http://www.newnownext.com/glaad-gay-childrens-books/05/2018/|website=www.newnownext.com|access-date=2019-09-04|archive-date=2020-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200207022732/http://www.newnownext.com/glaad-gay-childrens-books/05/2018/|dead-url=no}}</ref>,{{link-en|粉紅新聞|PinkNews}} <ref>{{Cite web|title=This children's book features a gay love story and it will warm your heart|url=https://www.pinknews.co.uk/2018/05/18/gay-childrens-book-prince-knight-love-story/|date=2018-05-18|website=PinkNews - Gay news, reviews and comment from the world's most read lesbian, gay, bisexual, and trans news service|language=en-GB|access-date=2019-09-04|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211024950/https://www.pinknews.co.uk/2018/05/18/gay-childrens-book-prince-knight-love-story/|dead-url=no}}</ref>, {{link-en|PopSugar| PopSugar}} <ref>{{Cite web|title=A Prince Meets His Knight in Shining Armor in This New, Inclusive Children's Book|url=https://www.popsugar.com/node/44869740|last=Messina|first=Victoria|date=2018-05-30|website=POPSUGAR Family|language=en-US|access-date=2019-09-04}}</ref>,[[今天_(NBC)|今天 (NBC)]] <ref>{{Cite web|title=16 picture books to help you raise kind, tolerant kids|url=https://www.today.com/parents/15-kids-picture-books-about-lgbtq-tolerance-celebrate-pride-t129950|website=TODAY.com|language=en|access-date=2019-09-04|archive-date=2021-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210316193004/https://www.today.com/parents/15-kids-picture-books-about-lgbtq-tolerance-celebrate-pride-t129950|dead-url=no}}</ref>和[[TheWrap|TheWrap]] <ref name="#1"/> 。

